.000Z","msg":"求片<br />\n學吓野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc100037158db2f95e7297889f473eac2b77390","tid":1084090,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"射唔射得切毒入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930eaf052fd638e72e59b924d4ac9ac547c97bd6","tid":1084090,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc6d1a0bc02b5ecd4b98ddff5a613c1fc960d87","tid":1084090,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZeyOOsJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZeyOOsJ.jpg&h=51cfe7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國亞利桑那州城市尤馬（Yuma），具有亞熱帶沙漠氣候，近來有科學家拍到在乾旱地區生存的更格盧鼠（kangaroo rat）遭沙漠響尾蛇猛然一咬，卻在電光石火間躍起躲避，並狠踹響尾蛇一腳將其踢開，外媒驚呼這一踢「連成龍都會嫉妒」！<br />\n<br />\n據《福斯新聞》報導，加州大學河濱分校生物學副教授海姆（Timothy Higham）發表了兩篇論文，詳細介紹沙漠響尾蛇和更格盧鼠令人難以置信的運動能力，他認為這兩種生物根本就是極限運動員。<br />\n<br />\n海姆表示，更格盧鼠依靠快速的反應時間來閃避蛇類襲擊，強而有力的後肢讓牠垂直跳躍的高度比自己身高多了好幾倍，而且跳躍途中還可使出飛踢以阻止蛇咬。<br />\n<br />\n海姆說，這種閃電般的快速動作，是動物在大自然中逃避掠食者的有效策略。蛇類捕食的突襲速度在100毫秒以內，但更格盧鼠只要38毫秒就能做出反應，並且在70毫秒內跳起逃生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=HTjX8YilcJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3DHTjX8YilcJg&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6nyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=aa6bf40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=HTjX8YilcJg</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T08:28:06.000Z","msg":"想睇冇放慢版本"},{"pid":"86873de8f02d2f7f3b5ec6866fbe87fcc796a266","tid":1084090,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23dafe89284db0b187df0b63231da784c11bb076","tid":1084090,"uid":92278,"like":14,"dislike":176,"score":-162,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"屌慢到咁都話快?<br />\n<br />\n阿婆都避得開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji